name.long: Infant formula, ABBOTT NUTRITION, SIMILAC, ISOMIL, ADVANCE with iron, powder, not reconstituted (formerly ROSS)

footnotes.text: Contains arachidonic acid (ARA, nutrient number 620) and docosahexaenoic acid (DHA, nutrient number 621), fatty acids found in human breast milk.
